===Adjective===
# [[forbidden]], [[prohibited]]

==English==
===Etymology===
A loan word with connotations of state [[authoritarianism]], derived from a perception of the German Empire under [[w:Wilhelm II|Wilhelm II]] or [[w:Nazi|Nazi]] Germany. In contemporary British usage its use can have a jocular subtext.
